144
00:11:39,914 --> 00:11:50,180
[SPEAKER_01]: anything that's shared with the city council would ultimately constitute to something that becomes a public record.

145
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:56,964
[SPEAKER_01]: And once a confidential matter becomes a public record, it can't be undone.

146
00:11:57,565 --> 00:11:59,066
