154
00:12:32,553 --> 00:12:45,997
[SPEAKER_06]: you know, if that's the easiest option versus some of the options being requiring more time to think through, that would be something that could get the information to us much more quickly than is currently happening.

155
00:12:46,037 --> 00:12:50,759
[SPEAKER_06]: And I think that would go a long way towards answering questions we have and making sure that we

156
