[SPEAKER_04]: They are responsible to make sure that, I mean, just like every municipality.

187
00:15:27,084 --> 00:15:29,465
[SPEAKER_10]: This group did ask for an independent audit last year.

188
00:15:31,008 --> 00:15:33,809
[SPEAKER_10]: We've never seen the report of the audit from other years either.

189
00:15:34,149 --> 00:15:34,389
[SPEAKER_10]: Okay.

190
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:48,281
[SPEAKER_04]: Municipalities in Massachusetts are required to have an independent audit every year.

191
00:15:48,481 --> 00:15:49,662
[SPEAKER_04]: That's Rizzelli and Clark.

192
00:15:49,722 --> 00:15:51,342
[SPEAKER_04]: They've been doing it for the last few years.

193
00:15:51,862 --> 00:15:53,743
[SPEAKER_04]: I don't know who did that before.

194
00:15:53,783 --> 00:15:54,663
[SPEAKER_04]: They did Nantucket.

195
00:15:55,103 --> 00:15:57,664
[SPEAKER_04]: Before Rizzelli and Clark, it was Powers and Sullivan.

196
00:15:58,684 --> 00:16:03,626
[SPEAKER_04]: All of that, the ACFR's annual comprehensive financial reports are all on the website.

197
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:10,395
[SPEAKER_10]: In the past, we've gotten a copy of those independent audits and I haven't seen one the last couple of years yet.

198
00:16:10,895 --> 00:16:11,616
[SPEAKER_10]: Okay.

199
00:16:11,896 --> 00:16:14,298
[SPEAKER_10]: I thought you weren't here.

200
00:16:14,778 --> 00:16:20,283
[SPEAKER_04]: No, I'll go on the website and print them out or I'll email the PDF to you.

201
00:16:20,543 --> 00:16:22,204
[SPEAKER_04]: Literally, they are on the website.

202
00:16:22,244 --> 00:16:26,287
[SPEAKER_04]: There's links on the finance page to go look at all of the stuff they do.

203
00:16:26,868 --> 00:16:31,531
[SPEAKER_04]: The annual comprehensive financial report and the single audit of federal funds.

204
00:16:31,551 --> 00:16:33,013
[SPEAKER_04]: Okay, thank you.

