374
00:31:42,851 --> 00:31:57,413
[SPEAKER_06]: how we can work through that, so that that process doesn't happen again so that it's not being generated so late, and we're not playing catch up, you know, that's what I'm talking about on the, on the go forward communication front so I really appreciate your comments on on being able to arrange that and set that up.

