00:58:02,082 --> 00:58:04,963
[SPEAKER_10]: How have the other budget directors done this in the past?

672
00:58:05,843 --> 00:58:07,503
[SPEAKER_10]: And why are we having such a problem now?

673
00:58:07,523 --> 00:58:18,887
[SPEAKER_10]: I mean, we've always, when we did our budgets, we've always saw a year to date spending and actuals.

674
00:58:20,387 --> 00:58:27,709
