[SPEAKER_04]: I want to do stump removal.

1390
01:56:55,480 --> 01:56:56,461
[SPEAKER_04]: I want to repave the streets.

1391
01:56:58,502 --> 01:57:13,114
[SPEAKER_04]: If you say, if you have the room to use revenue replacement for that, that means that you can do what you want without having it be in a specific ARPA budget bucket that has strings attached.

1392
01:57:14,015 --> 01:57:20,801
[SPEAKER_04]: It doesn't mean that we have to use revenue replacement for funding the city's budget for the next year.

1393
01:57:22,182 --> 01:57:25,365
[SPEAKER_04]: That's, we can, but we don't need to.

1394
01:57:26,938 --> 01:57:27,839
[SPEAKER_04]: it doesn't constrain it.

1395
