1404
01:58:36,996 --> 01:58:52,789
[SPEAKER_04]: I mean, some of it's unavoidable, but some of it, but you know, we need to look down the road, not just at fiscal 2024, but 25, 26 out there and see where we need to, you know, how we're gonna make that work.

1405
